flowchart LR
REQ[Request] --> ASSESS[Risk and Impact]
ASSESS --> APPROVE{Approved?}
APPROVE -- No --> REWORK[Rework or Reject]
APPROVE -- Yes --> IMPLEMENT[Implement]
IMPLEMENT --> VALIDATE[Validate]
VALIDATE --> SUCCESS{Successful?}
SUCCESS -- No --> ROLLBACK[Rollback]
SUCCESS -- Yes --> CLOSE[Close and Update CMDB]
